SelectInputSearchComponent
components.templateData:
<ng-select 
    [(ngModel)]="selectedItem"
    [ngClass]="classes" 
    (change)="onChange($event)"
    [hideSelected]="true"
    [editableSearchTerm]="true"
    [placeholder]="placeholderText"
>
    <ng-option class="option" *ngFor="let item of items" [value]="item">
        {{item}}
    </ng-option>
</ng-select>

</ng-select>
